I've released the Lightroom preset, "USETSU presets by Takashi Yasui". Alongside this, I've also published articles detailing the background of its creation and an explanation about the presets. Please check it out via the link in my profile. #USETSUpresets

If you purchase the photobook "PERSONAL WORK" on the official site along with the presets, you will receive a 20% discount. Additionally, for those who have previously purchased the photobook, by entering the coupon code "P601NAJWDA11" at the checkout, you'll also get a 20% off.
